column2: select a.target_id, a.m_h, a.m_h_err, a.alpha_m, a.alpha_m_err, log(#. + # * a.alpha_m) as salaris from aspcapStar a   join mydb.highfeh m on a.target_id = m.id_#  where a.m_h > # and a.alpha_m > #   and a.m_h + log(#. + # * a.alpha_m) > #     and a.m_h + log(#. + # * a.alpha_m) < #   order by salaris
